videos.description: Sam Darnold puts it in the perfect spot for Deontay Burnett on the 32-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Darnold floats it up for Burnett for the score

videos.description: Manny Wilkins evades pressure and launches it downfield to K'Neal Harry for a 70-yard gain that sets up an Arizona State field goal.
videos.headline: Harry goes up and gets it for a huge gain

videos.description: Manny Wilkins' incomplete pass goes out-of-bounds but Sam Darnold is there to make the grab.
videos.headline: Darnold tries to be receiver from the sideline

videos.description: Tyler Vaughns breaks away and dives towards the pylon for the 42-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Vaughns shows shades of Reggie Bush on TD

videos.description: Ronald Jones II finds a hole and takes off down the right sideline for the 67-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Jones takes it to the crib

videos.description: Sam Darnold shows off his elusiveness and picks up 39 yards on the run.
videos.headline: Darnold escapes the pocket for the 39-yard gain

videos.description: Sam Darnold coughs up his 7th lost fumble on the season as Christian Sam forces the turnover for Arizona State.
videos.headline: Darnold turns it over for Trojans

videos.description: Tyler Petite breaks tackles and stumbles to midfield for the 37-yard gain.
videos.headline: Darnold finds Petite over the middle for 37 yards

videos.description: Sam Darnold fires a perfect strike to Tyler Vaughns for a 19-yard touchdown. Also on the play, Dasmond Tautalatasi is ejected for targeting.
videos.headline: Darnold threads the needle for 3rd TD pass

videos.description: Manny Wilkins tosses up the Hail Mary that gets deflected and Kyle Williams dives to make the catch at the goal line. The play is reviewed and called a touchdown.  Both teams have to come back on the field for the extra point.
videos.headline: Arizona State pulls of Hail Mary to end half

videos.description: Arizona State head coach Todd Graham says the team has to come out better for the second half.
videos.headline: ASU trails 31-10 but has momentum going into halftime

videos.description: Clay Helton is happy with the Trojans' offensive performance during the first half against the Sun Devils.
videos.headline: USC takes big lead into halftime led by Darnold

videos.description: Manny Wilkins finishes off the opening drive for the Sun Devils in the second half with a touchdown.
videos.headline: Benjamin's run sets up 1-yard TD score

videos.description: Ronald Jones II finds space and shows off his speed for his second 60+ yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Jones breaks loose in the open field

videos.description: Ronald Jones II is showing out against the Sun Devils, he has 18 carries for 216 yards.
videos.headline: Jones goes over the 200-yard mark after this 20-yard run

videos.description: Sam Darnold makes his second catch of the night from the sideline, showing off his vertical.
videos.headline: Darnold might have a future but not at QB

videos.description: Blake Barnett is picked off by Ykili Ross off the tip and returns it 37 yards for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Ross caps off win for Trojans

videos.description: Sam Darnold tosses three touchdowns as the offense explodes for over 600 yards in a win over Arizona State.
videos.headline: Darnold leads USC to big victory

videos.description: Ronald Jones II busts out for 218 yards on the ground as USC wins 48-17 over Arizona State.
videos.headline: Jones breaks open for over 200 yards in win

videos.description: Clay Helton discusses USC's big win over Arizona State as they continue to chase the Pac-12 title.
videos.headline: Helton proud of team's effort after big win

videos.description: Anthony Becht and Beth Mowins break down the keys for USC in their big win over Arizona State led by Sam Darnold and Ronald Jones II.
videos.headline: USC dominates Arizona State with a 48-17 win
